Hello, this is David Rogers please?

Hi David, my name is Julie Kelly.

Thank you, Julie. How can I assist you today?

I received the wrong item in my order, and I wanted to get this sorted out.

I'm sorry to hear that, Julie. Let's get this resolved for you. Could you provide me with the order number, please?

Sure, the order number is two three four five.

Thank you. Could you also let me know the item you received and the item you were expecting?

I received a yacht anchor, but I was expecting a navigation system.

I apologize for the mix-up, Julie. I will ensure we get the correct navigation system sent to you right away.

Thank you very much for bringing this to our attention, Julie. We appreciate your patience and trust in us. Have a great day!
